research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Caldwell city, TX, include the Mayor and five Alderpersons. The Alderpersons appear to serve at-large, as no specific ward or district designations were found in the search results. Kavon Novak also holds the role of Mayor Pro Tem. Information was gathered from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory, Texas State Directory Online, and the City of Caldwell's official website.
